Glencore Appoints Callow as Chief Executive of Its Mopani Unit in Zambia

-- B y   A n t h o n y   M u k w i t a
-- 
2011-07-29T09:22:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-29/glencore-appoints-callow-as-chief-executive-of-its-mopani-unit-in-zambia.html
Glencore International Plc’s Mopani
Copper Mines Plc unit in Zambia appointed Danny Callow as chief
executive officer, Mopani said in a statement published in the
Lusaka-based Post newspaper today.  Callow replaces Emmanuel Mutati, who becomes chairman of
Mopani’s board, the company said. Callow joins Mopani from
Mutanda Mining, a Glencore unit in the Democratic Republic of
Congo, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anthony Mukwita at 
